1. *Zli* ljudi su mi ukrali bicikl. (Evil people stole my bike.)
2. On je *zločinac* koji je ubio svoju ženu. (He is an *evil-doer* who killed his wife.)
3. Činilo joj se da je neki *zli* duh u kući. (She felt like there was some *evil* spirit in the house.)
4. *Zlo* je uvijek bilo prisutno u ovom gradu. (Evil has always been present in this city.)
5. *Zla* sudbina me je zadesila. (An *evil* fate has befallen me.)
6. Nije dobro biti *zloban* prema drugima. (It's not good to be *malicious* towards others.)
7. Bio je *zlonameran* i stalno je širio laži o drugima. (He was *malevolent* and constantly spread lies about others.)
8. Ponekad su naši najbolji prijatelji takođe *zli* prema nama. (Sometimes our best friends can also be *mean* to us.)